                    <td background="images/rtb2.jpg" width="627" height="38"><table width="95%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" height="19"><tr><td style="height: 19px" width="100%" align="center"><span id="lbtitle" style="color:Black;font-size:Large;font-weight:bold;">我校全市文科状元易莉萍同学接受记者专访</span></td></tr></table></td></tr>
                    <tr><td colspan="2" background="images/bg2.jpg" width="727" height="19">
                        </td></tr>
